-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-249-hamas-cannot-rule-gaza-after-war-top-u-s-official-says/00000190-0829-d667-abf0-6ceb14f90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谈论了一场对抗伊朗核武器的精彩比赛——仅此而已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-talks-a-good-game-against-iranian-nukes-and-thats-it/00000190-06ff-d5ad-ad93-26ff98a10000</link><description>以色列总理从未制定过一致的政策来对抗伊朗核计划，包括2018年他让特朗普退出核协议时。内塔尼亚胡在国会的演讲中，预计会有更多诸如“西方正面临毁灭”之类的咆哮</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-talks-a-good-game-against-iranian-nukes-and-thats-it/00000190-06ff-d5ad-ad93-26ff98a10000</guid></item><item><title>皮尤调查显示，随着加沙战争的拖延，拜登在以色列人中的支持率下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-popularity-among-israelis-drops-as-gaza-war-drags-on-pew-survey-shows/00000190-075f-d0f9-a1d5-d77f6cd90000</link><description>对美国总统的信心从 68% 下降至 57%，仅领先特朗普 3 个百分点</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-popularity-among-israelis-drops-as-gaza-war-drags-on-pew-survey-shows/00000190-075f-d0f9-a1d5-d77f6cd90000</guid></item><item><title>包括哈马斯成员在内的四名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/four-palestinians-including-hamas-member-killed-by-idf-troops-in-west-bank/00000190-0746-da02-a1dc-ff4f61240000</link><description>在拉马拉附近的一个村庄被杀的巴勒斯坦人中包括一名哈马斯军事部门的成员，他曾在以色列监狱服刑 20 年</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 14:46:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/four-palestinians-including-hamas-member-killed-by-idf-troops-in-west-bank/00000190-0746-da02-a1dc-ff4f61240000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争使以色列立法者在征兵法案上存在分歧；利库德集团成员呼吁解雇加兰特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/isr